'''新加坡杜莎夫人蜡像馆'''，({{lang-en|Madame Tussauds Singapore}}), 是位于[[新加坡|新加坡]][[圣淘沙|圣淘沙]]的一个蜡像馆，是属于[[杜莎夫人蜡像馆|杜莎夫人蜡像馆]]旗下的分馆。

==历史==
于2014年10月25日开馆，是亚洲地区第七家场馆。美国流行歌手[[凯蒂·佩里|凯蒂·佩里]]也拥有一尊蜡像并出席了开幕仪式。<ref>{{cite news|title=Visitors impressed by Madame Tussauds Singapore but let down by suspended ride|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/visitors-impressed-by-madame-tussauds-singapore-but-let-down-by-suspended-ride|accessdate=29 December 2015|work=[[The_Straits_Times|The Straits Times]]|date=26 October 2014|archive-date=2020-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715153657/https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/visitors-impressed-by-madame-tussauds-singapore-but-let-down-by-suspended-ride|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Madame Tussauds opens in Singapore|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/business-29875405|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=13 August 2014|accessdate=2016-10-15|archive-date=2016-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161226150255/http://www.bbc.com/news/business-29875405|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Ansuya Harjani|title=Katy Perry joins star line-up for Singapore Madame Tussauds|url=http://www.cnbc.com/id/42551921|accessdate=8 April 2015|publisher=CNBC|date=9 December 2013|ref=cnbc|archive-date=2015-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150411052604/http://www.cnbc.com/id/42551921|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

